{"tid":1130881,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[有冇人睇？] 總決算！平成紅白歌合戰","createTime":"2019-04-29T10:34:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T13:33:28.000Z","uid":14788,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"12739ad08790e4b59fc7ea7fbfdae7ea1fd63054","tid":1130881,"uid":14788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T10:34:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JLWhgnb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJLWhgnb.jpg&h=76a797e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每年除夕夜在NHK播出的《NHK紅白歌合戰》將在即將改為「令和」之前4月29日的晚上播出回首平成的30年間的《紅白》節目《總決算！平成紅白歌會》。主持人為櫻井翔以及小野文恵播音員。<br />\n節目分為兩部。第1部位平成30年間的名歌唱，名場面彙集播出。代表平成的紅白的3組藝人，嵐，北島三郎，松田聖子齊聚，講述感人的回憶以及現在才可以說出口的軼事。<br />\n<br />\n■播出<br />\n1部、2部皆為綜合電視台：4月29日（月・祝)）<br />\n第1部 晚7：３０～8：55<br />\n第2部 晚10：00～11：30<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd3d6eaa23b7bfbd8924882ced88121c3ec68a96","tid":1130881,"uid":14788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T10:34:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gumQBsS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgumQBsS.png&h=e1ede512&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f476ab23826334975d3e8ffebac3685d7130afc","tid":1130881,"uid":11067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T10:35:03.000Z","msg":"有冇歌單<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d34db6471dfe8061468196318ec60f4364cd30d5","tid":1130881,"uid":14788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f476ab23826334975d3e8ffebac3685d7130afc","tid":1130881,"uid":11067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T10:35:03.000Z","msg":"有冇歌單<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T10:36:17.000Z","msg":"搵唔到呀，連直播link都好少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b84967af0de93fea7bf032660046295a03b07ab","tid":1130881,"uid":14788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T10:36:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.nhk.or.jp/kouhaku/heisei/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nhk.or.jp%2Fkouhaku%2Fheisei%2Findex.html&d=5ezJA%2FdytRM7iHrFGdkn9YR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=f87cd69b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nhk.or.jp/kouhaku/heisei/index.html</a>"},{"pid":"415a24518a7a511bbf805ecf22e4c76a8d56df32","tid":1130881,"uid":14788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T10:38:40.000Z","msg":"第1部は感動の名唱名場面集決定版<br />\n第1部は平成30年間の名歌唱名場面を集めてお届けします。<br />\n平成の紅白を代表する3組のアーティスト、嵐・北島三郎・松田聖子がスタジオに集い、感動の思い出や、今だから話せるエピソードを語っていただきます。<br />\n<br />\n第2部は、伝説の紅白スペシャルステージ＆ハプニング集！<br />\n番組は2部に分かれて放送。第２部では、「全部まとめて平成紅白伝説」と題して、平成30年間の「紅白でしか見られないスペシャルステージ」の名場面やハプニング集を紹介していきます。平成最後の紅白・総合司会を務めた内村光良と、平成で4回ウラトークのMCを務めたバナナマンがスタジオに集結。紅白「オモテとウラ」の司会者が、紅白名シーンの舞台裏も交えながらにぎやかに、楽しくお届けします。"},{"pid":"4e5644cb1145b98843a169068000f524a3a5cad6","tid":1130881,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T10:40:20.000Z","msg":"平成年代 紅白邊啲片段最經典？"},{"pid":"21b4d23105c1112c38458620df8b9ed10e68105a","tid":1130881,"uid":14788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e5644cb1145b98843a169068000f524a3a5cad6","tid":1130881,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T10:40:20.000Z","msg":"平成年代 紅白邊啲片段最經典？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T10:46:48.000Z","msg":"應該就係啦，搵人做主持播埋片<br />\n順便J下嵐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下半場唔知有冇人唱"},{"pid":"1c8c37b8c276047baa86bcf9108954adb93dde32","tid":1130881,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T10:47:46.000Z","msg":"北島三郎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=